---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const updated = 'June 21, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — revpdf"
  description="How revpdf handles your data: it doesn't. Everything stays on your device."
>
  <article class="legal section">
    <a class="back" href="/">← Back to home</a>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <p class="lead">
      revpdf is built to be private. It has no accounts and no servers, and it does not collect,
      transmit or sell your personal data. Everything you do in the app stays on your device.
    </p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Nothing.</strong> revpdf does not have user accounts and does not send your documents,
      highlights, reading progress or settings anywhere. There is no analytics SDK and no advertising
      in the app.
    </p>

    <h2>Where your data lives</h2>
    <p>
      Documents you import, your highlights, bookmarks, reading position and preferences are stored
      locally on your device only. Uninstalling the app removes this data.
    </p>

    <h2>Permissions</h2>
    <p>
      revpdf asks only for access to files you explicitly pick (so it can open them) and, optionally,
      screen brightness (so it can dim the screen for reading). It does not access your contacts,
      location or photos beyond the files you choose.
    </p>

    <h2>In-app web search</h2>
    <p>
      When you select text and use the optional search feature, your query is sent to the search
      engine you chose (for example Google or DuckDuckGo) in an in-app browser. That request is
      governed by the chosen provider’s own privacy policy. This feature is entirely optional and can
      be disabled in Settings.
    </p>

    <h2>This website</h2>
    <p>
      revpdf.in is a static informational site. It does not set tracking cookies. Fonts are loaded
      from Google Fonts, which may receive your IP address as part of serving those files.
    </p>

    <h2>Children</h2>
    <p>revpdf is suitable for general audiences and does not knowingly collect data from anyone.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>
      If this policy changes, we will update the date above. Material changes will be reflected on
      this page.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Privacy questions? Reach out via <a href="https://bksh.site">bksh.site</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .legal h1 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 44px);
  }
  .legal .lead {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--on-surface-variant);
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }
</style>
